=== GRAVITY_WELL ===
# id: 8
# title: The Gravity Well
# chinese_title: 重力井
# category: Discovery
# mode: dungeon

A section of the station has a localized gravity anomaly. Objects float lazily near the ceiling while others are pinned to the floor with crushing force. In the center of the disturbance, a small device hovers, perfectly balanced between the competing forces.

* [Navigate the gravity fields to reach the device]
  ~ gain_radical("力")
  "力" (lì) — power, strength, force
* [Toss objects to map the safe path]
  ~ gain_xp(15)
  "飞" (fēi) — to fly, to float
* [Avoid the anomaly entirely]
  ~ nothing
  "重" (zhòng) — heavy, weight
